<style>
#shopify-section-{{ section.id }}{margin-top:{{section.settings.padding_top  }}px;margin-bottom:{{section.settings.padding_bottom  }}px;}
.recommend-plan{gap:9px;align-items: stretch;}
.recommend-plan .left {
  width: 33%; /* 与右侧比例协调 */
  display: flex;
  align-items: center; /* 垂直居中 */
}

.recommend-plan .left .image-wrapper {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}

.recommend-plan .left img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-top-left-radius: 25px;
  border-bottom-left-radius: 25px;
}
.recommend-plan .right{width:67%}
.recommend-plan .right-box{ display: flex;height: 120px; width: 120px;border-radius: 50%;justify-content: center; align-items: center;
 position: relative;left: 50%;transform: translateX(-50%); background: #fff;}
.recommend-plan .right-box .image-wrapper{position:relative;height:67px}
.recommend-plan .right-box .image-wrapper img{ height: 100%;width: 100%; object-fit:cover}
.recommend-plan .right ul{  flex-wrap: wrap;    gap: 9px;}
.recommend-plan .right ul li{ flex: 0 0 calc(50% - 9px); background: #F1F1F1;padding:33px 26px;text-align:center }
.recommend-plan .right ul li:nth-child(2){border-top-right-radius:25px}
.recommend-plan .right ul li:nth-child(4){border-bottom-right-radius:25px}
.recommend-plan .right ul li .tit,.recommend-plan .right ul li .links{margin-top:15px;line-height: 29.694px;font-size: 22px;font-weight:400}
.recommend-plan .right ul li .tit{color: #000;}
.recommend-plan .right ul li .links{color: #3250C3;}
.recommend-plan .right ul li .description{margin-top:4px;line-height: 20px;font-size: 16px;color: #7C7C7C;  display: -webkit-box;
  -webkit-box-orient: vertical;-webkit-line-clamp: 6;overflow: hidden;text-overflow: ellipsis;}

 #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} a {
    color: #3250C3;
    text-decoration:underline;
}
.gungentxt-div{
padding-top:120px;
}

.gungentxt{

line-height: 20px;font-size: 16px;
}

.gungentxt strong{
display: block;
text-align: center;
line-height: 56px;font-size: 46px;
}
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }}{margin-top:{{section.settings.padding_top | divided_by: 2  }}px;margin-bottom:{{section.settings.padding_bottom | divided_by: 2  }}px;}
    .recommend-plan{flex-flow: column;}
    .recommend-plan .right ul li{ flex: 0 0 calc(50% - 5px); padding: 22px 22px 25px 22px;}
    .recommend-plan .left,
    .recommend-plan .right {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .recommend-plan .left img {
      border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;
      border-top-left-radius: 15px;
      border-top-right-radius: 15px;
    }
    .recommend-plan .right-box{width:5rem;height:5rem}
    .recommend-plan .right-box .image-wrapper{position:relative;height:2.7rem}
    .recommend-plan .right-box .image-wrapper img{ height: 100%;width: 100%; object-fit:cover}
    .recommend-plan .right ul li{ flex: 0 0 calc(100% - 9px);}
    .left .image-wrapper{display:none;}
    .recommend-plan .right ul li:nth-child(2){border-top-right-radius:0px}
    .recommend-plan .right ul li:nth-child(3){border-bottom-left-radius:15px}
    .recommend-plan .right ul li:nth-child(4){border-bottom-right-radius:15px}
    .recommend-plan .right ul li .tit,.recommend-plan .right ul li .links{margin-top:9px;line-height:15px;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom:6px;}
    .recommend-plan .right ul li .description{margin-top:0px;line-height: 15px;font-size: 12px;}

    .gungentxt{
      line-height: 15px;font-size: 12px;
      }
    .gungentxt-div{
      padding-top:60px;
    }
    .gungentxt strong{
      line-height: 34px;font-size: 28px;
    }

    .recommend-plan .right ul li .description{-webkit-line-clamp: 10;}
  }
</style>
{% liquid
    assign motion_delay = 50
%}
<div class="section page-width section--padding flex recommend-plan">
    <div class="left">
          {% if section.settings.image != blank %}
          
            <div class="image-wrapper">
              <picture>
                <source
                  media="(max-width: 749px)"
                  srcset="
                    {{ section.settings.image_mobile | img_url: '800x' }} 1x,
                    {{ section.settings.image_mobile | img_url: '1600x' }} 2x
                  "
                >
                <source
                  media="(min-width: 750px)"
                  srcset="
                    {{ section.settings.image | img_url: '1200x' }} 1x,
                    {{ section.settings.image | img_url: '2400x' }} 2x
                  "
                >
                <img
                  src="{{ section.settings.image | img_url: '1200x' }}"
                  alt="{{ section.settings.image | escape }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                  width="{{ section.settings.image.width }}"
                  height="{{ section.settings.image.height }}"
                >
              </picture>
             </div>
            {% else %}
              {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'placeholder-svg' }}
            {% endif %}
    </div>
    <div class="flex right list">
      <div class="list-box">
      <ul class="flex">
        {% for block in section.blocks %}
        <li>
           {% if block.settings.image != blank %}
              <div class="right-box">
            <div class="image-wrapper">
              <picture>
                <source
                  media="(max-width: 749px)"
                  srcset="
                    {{ block.settings.image_mobile | img_url: '800x' }} 1x,
                    {{ block.settings.image_mobile | img_url: '1600x' }} 2x
                  "
                >
                <source
                  media="(min-width: 750px)"
                  srcset="
                    {{ block.settings.image | img_url: '1200x' }} 1x,
                    {{ block.settings.image | img_url: '2400x' }} 2x
                  "
                >
                <img
                  src="{{ block.settings.image | img_url: '1200x' }}"
                  alt="{{ block.settings.image | escape }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                  width="{{ block.settings.image.width }}"
                  height="{{ block.settings.image.height }}"
                >
              </picture>
             </div>
           </div>
            {% else %}
              {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'placeholder-svg' }}
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.image != blank %}
                <h2 class="tit">{{ block.settings.title }}</h2>
            {% endif %}
             {% if block.settings.links != blank %}
                <div class="links">{{ block.settings.links }}</div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.description != blank %}
                <div class="description">{{ block.settings.description }}</div>
            {% endif %}
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="section page-width gungentxt-div">
  <div class="gungentxt"><strong>Teilnahmebedingungen: </strong>
<br>1. Nur Kunden mit mindestens einer abgeschlossenen Bestellung dürfen als Empfehlende an der Aktion teilnehmen.
<br>2. Wenn jemand über deinen Empfehlungslink bestellt und innerhalb von 30 Tagen nach Versand keine Rückgabe/Rückerstattung macht, kannst du deine 50€ Cashback beantragen. Schreib einfach an: <a href="/pages/contact-us">service@indevolt.com</a>.
<br>3. Die empfohlene Person erhält einen Rabattcode im Wert von 50€ (gültig für Bestellungen über 399€). Der Code ist 3 Tage lang gültig.
<br>4. Der erhaltene Rabattcode kann nur mit einem weiteren Gutschein der Website kombiniert werden (z. B. Newsletter-Gutschein oder Aktionsgutschein).
<br>5. Eine Kombination mit anderen Partner- oder Affiliate-Gutscheinen (z. B. exklusive Codes für YouTuber, Influencer oder Produkttester) ist ausgeschlossen.
</div>
</div>
